    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Study of ethics inspired and informed by religious doctrine, faith, and experience, also the study of religious doctrine and commitment with reference to ethics.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
